window.docContents[142].resolve({"/____________/______/#zh-basictypes-string-h010":{"contents":"Replaces the character at position p in the string s with the result of applying f to that\ncharacter.If both the replacement character and the replaced character are 7-bit ASCII characters and the\nstring is not shared, then it is updated in-place and not copied.Examples:* (\"abc\".pos ⟨1⟩ (by decide)).modify Char.toUpper (by decide) = \"aBc\"\n\nReturns the byte at the position pos of a string.\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009基本类型\u0009弦乐\u0009API 参考\u0009职位","header":"20.8.4.4.3. 修改","id":"/____________/______/#zh-basictypes-string-h010"},"/____________/_______________/#zh-basictypes-fin-h004":{"contents":"The greatest value of Fin (n+1), namely n.Examples:* Fin.last 4 = (4 : Fin 5)* (Fin.last 0).val = (0 : Nat)\n\nThe successor, with an increased bound.This differs from adding 1, which instead wraps around.Examples:* (2 : Fin 3).succ = (3 : Fin 4)* (2 : Fin 3) + 1 = (0 : Fin 3)\n\nThe predecessor of a non-zero element of Fin (n+1), with the bound decreased.Examples:* (4 : Fin 8).pred (by decide) = (3 : Fin 7)* (1 : Fin 2).pred (by decide) = (0 : Fin 1)\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009基本类型\u0009有限自然数\u0009API 参考","header":"20.3.3.1. 建造","id":"/____________/_______________/#zh-basictypes-fin-h004"}});